{"tid":134796,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「紅軍小學」崛起：學生穿軍服、大唱紅歌","createTime":"2017-02-25T18:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T04:20:23.000Z","uid":53060,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad65761c6a68d5829412f73b69f29e2c520b3c89","tid":134796,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/02/24/99/3215092.jpg&amp;s=Y&amp;x=3&amp;y=0&amp;sw=951&amp;sh=617&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F02%2F24%2F99%2F3215092.jpg%26s%3DY%26x%3D3%26y%3D0%26sw%3D951%26sh%3D617%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=7f202935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一群孩子穿著當年紅軍的灰色軍服，佩戴紅領巾、紅五角星軍帽，大聲唱起紅軍歌曲。根據《Daily Mail Online》報導，貴州省遵義市楊得志紅軍小學的學生們，每天都穿著紅軍制服上學，接受「紅色教育」。<br />\n<br />\n楊得志小學建立於清朝末年，已經有100年以上的歷史，而自從2008年，該所學校被劃歸紅軍小學建設工程，不僅<span style=\"color: red;\">校名被改為「紅軍小學」</span>，學生們每天都得接受紅色教育。<br />\n<br />\n截至去年，在大陸已經有200多所像這樣的紅軍學校。2007年中共前領導人的家人發起成立紅軍小學建設工程後，由「紅二代」出資成立的「紅軍小學」，近年來<span style=\"color: red;\">快速擴張到大陸各省</span>。"},{"pid":"dddf30ff4f5894867d7b59abac743b30f11561aa","tid":134796,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:00:48.000Z","msg":"在楊得志紅軍小學讀書的孩子們，<span style=\"color: red;\">每天的生活、學習都離不開中國共產黨</span>，接受極端的愛國教育。外界批評，紅軍小學進行的簡直就是洗腦教育，讓這麼小的孩子心靈打上共產黨的烙印，可能讓他們失去創新與獨立思考能力，影響孩子的成長。"},{"pid":"95e10eb99c1b6918e35699622cf1acc291e59b06","tid":134796,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:02:14.000Z","msg":"不得了"},{"pid":"88e7f0f015c63369510fdad396ca508fb5e81a29","tid":134796,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:02:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7332/2306001#prettyPhoto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7332%2F2306001%23prettyPhoto&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=dc0bc2f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7332/2306001#prettyPhoto</a>"},{"pid":"dbf7859a3fc78c2840a3b5ad58ba42ba3155ad3f","tid":134796,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.news.xinhuanet.com/gongyi/2014-10/29/127154366_14145511076021n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.xinhuanet.com%2Fgongyi%2F2014-10%2F29%2F127154366_14145511076021n.jpg&h=739dd310&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ea8f1af96c6d9e9a0a74f244ec578edc1b760cc","tid":134796,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.youth.cn/wztt/201211/W020121118478004301032.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.youth.cn%2Fwztt%2F201211%2FW020121118478004301032.jpg&h=16f3cc34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d1ca052aeb081045e6b682fb52c1359ff9a831e","tid":134796,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://news.xinhuanet.com/gongyi/2014-10/29/127154366_14145511076021n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.xinhuanet.com%2Fgongyi%2F2014-10%2F29%2F127154366_14145511076021n.jpg&h=b6bb7e09&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"dc28c12822866d9cb59271f338f8b5cc9227b020","tid":134796,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:08:20.000Z","msg":"民革2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3130bc29bdfb70cddcb3090b86c2d22d156d00fe","tid":134796,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在楊得志紅軍小學讀書的孩子們，每天的生活、學習都離不開中國共產黨，接受極端的愛國教育。外界批評，紅軍小學進行的簡直就是洗腦教育，讓這麼小的孩子心靈打上共產黨的烙印，<span style=\"color: red;\">可能讓他們失去創新與獨立思考能力</span>，影響孩子的成長。</blockquote><br />\n俾你